---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Delete Account — The Yips" description="Request deletion of your The Yips account and data.">
  <main style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 1.5rem; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; color: #e5e5e5; line-height: 1.7;">
    <a href="/" style="color: #4ADE80; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem;">← Back to The Yips</a>

    <h1 style="margin-top: 2rem; color: #ffffff; font-size: 2rem;">Delete Your Account</h1>
    <p>You can request deletion of your The Yips account and all associated data at any time.</p>

    <h2 style="color: #ffffff; margin-top: 2rem;">What gets deleted</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Your account and profile information</li>
      <li>All rounds, hole entries, and shot data</li>
      <li>Club bag configuration</li>
      <li>API keys and usage records</li>
      <li>Any other data tied to your account</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="color: #9ca3af; font-size: 0.9rem;">Deletion is permanent and cannot be undone.</p>

    <h2 style="color: #ffffff; margin-top: 2rem;">How to request deletion</h2>
    <p>Send an email to <a href="mailto:mitch@undeadops.dev?subject=Account Deletion Request&body=Please delete my The Yips account. My registered email address is: " style="color: #4ADE80;">mitch@undeadops.dev</a> with the subject line <strong>Account Deletion Request</strong> and include the email address associated with your account.</p>
    <p>We will process your request and confirm deletion within 30 days.</p>

    <div style="margin-top: 2.5rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; background: rgba(74,222,128,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(74,222,128,0.2); border-radius: 8px;">
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">
        <strong style="color: #4ADE80;">Email:</strong>
        <a href="mailto:mitch@undeadops.dev?subject=Account Deletion Request&body=Please delete my The Yips account. My registered email address is: " style="color: #e5e5e5; margin-left: 8px;">mitch@undeadops.dev</a>
      </p>
      <p style="margin: 0.5rem 0 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">
        <strong style="color: #4ADE80;">Subject:</strong>
        <span style="margin-left: 8px;">Account Deletion Request</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
